PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of certain persons as directors of the Canadian Commercial Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (Helen Gillespie, Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario, in the place of Frank Petrie, whose term has expired; and André Trépanier, Montreal, Quebec, in the place of John M. Banigan, whose term has expired)
